text:
Pengamalaman seru bisa menginap di Ashley hotel. Kami memesan kamar eksekutif karena kamarnya yg luas, dengan 2 bed ukuran besar menambah kenyamanan liburan keluarga kami. Tersedia coffee maker, kulkas, mini brangkas, dsb. Sempat ada sedikit trobel dengan lemari, tp semua tertangani dengan teknisi hotel yg cepat tanggap. 

Sarapannya enak enak, dengan varian menu yg cukup beragam. Buah puding, sereal, juice, dsb. Ada beberapa masukan untuk resto, menu mungkin bisa menambah varian buah dan bubur ayam, Membuat sign area toaster lbh jelas dan berwarna agar mudah terbaca, dan mengganti dispenser sereal agar mudah digunakan, terutama di sereal yg warna warni, agak kesulitan memutar tuas dispensernya, apalagi jk anak anak yg menggunakan. But overall, kita sangat senang dan puas bisa menginap disni.

Oh ya, ini pengalaman kami yg ke 2 menginap di Ashley hotel, hotel yg sangat nyaman di tengah kesibukan ibu kota. Stafnya ramah dan sangat membantu. Semoga bisa kembali menginap di ashley. Thankyou

text:
Ashley hotel tanah abang interior dan suasana hotelnya saya sangat suka sih dan bagus serta mewah tapi tetap hangat suasananya, namun ada beberapa hal yang perlu di note dan diketahui ya sebelum stay : 
Kalau saya ada salah bisa koreksi (Hal hal negatif dari hotel)
1. Permintaan trip advisor terkesan dipaksa, karena dimintakan isi sebelum stay hanya saat check in pdhal tamu belum merasakan over all stay, *tdk perlu saya sebutkan staff anda yang seperti itu, namun semuanya sepertinya seperti itu, karena review yg saya baca hanya review lobby tdk ada review detail terkait kamar resto dll

2. Tidak ada fasilitas room service utk hotel ini , smoga kedepannya sudah ada room service

3. Kamarnya dindingnya tipis, pada pagi hari subuh terdengar suara alarm HP dari kamar sebelah, dan jelas sekali itu alarm dari HP, sampai kamar sebelah saya (kebetulan saya pesan 2 kamar) terdengar juga

4. Pada saat check in, salah satu kunci kamar tidak bisa dibuka sampai menunggu  lama sudah telp resepsionis, bulak balik baru bisa teratasi

5. Kolam renang air nya kurang bersih

Hal yang positif : 
1. Kamar cukup nyaman, ac ckup dingin, air panas cukup baik

2. Kolam renang suasanya sangat bagus, hanya agak kotor saja airnya

3. Makanan breakfast saya kasih 1000 bintang, karena ini breakfast yg terbaik hampir selevel dengan padma Hotel Groups, namun tdk ada room service itu disayangkan

owner_response.title: Tanggapan Pemilik

text:
Staff 10/10 :  Fauzan /  Jefri / Jenny  plus others -  They ensure that you were not left alone.  They call the room ensure that everything in order.  Even at the buffet area they comes and equerry about food and stay.  Staff who care for you. 

Location 10/10 . Very Strategically located. Just 5 min walk to Tanah Abang Shopping area.  10 minutes to Tamrin  City Shopping. 12  Minutes to grand Indonesia Mall and Sarinah 5 min walk where you have lot of Japanese food, Burger King, Starbucks,  Pizza, Street food, and Money exchange(Price is not so good - Exchange from Grand Indonesian Mall)

Room :  10/10 - Superb room, Spacious, Comfy feather feeling pillow bed,  LED TV, with Netflix, Prime,   Water coffee machine 

Toilet : 10/10 - Big and sparkling clean.  Hot water shower is great.

Breakfast : 10/10  Varieties of food option.   Soup, Rice, Fish, Chicken, Beef, Coronate, Bread, Jam, Pickles, Coffee tea Milk flakes, Fruits, Puddings.. you name it they have it.   -
You can also have ala- carte food   for lunch and Dinner with additional cost.  Best place to have breakfast is  pool side.

Hotel Theme :  10/10.  I appreciate the hotel interior designer - Its Mixture of  Granite rock and Mahogany theme   Warm white lights evenly matching the indoor show pieces. 

Gym  :  10/10  Open 24 Hours,  you can enjoy when no is there,  sufficient equipment - all in good condition including attached washroom and shower.  

Swimming pool :  9.99/10 Main attraction to the hotel theme is the pool, 1,2 Meter, they supply tower, and my daughter enjoyed a lot in the pool.  The water was too cold.  Could have been better if temperate controlled water This could be a cherry on a cake.   May be if the Hotel Management thinking of an improvement  they can consider this.  But its awesome pool.

Exterior : When you enter, you feel the hotel atmosphere from outer design itself.  Especially in the evening when LED strip lights are on.

Wifi : 10/10 : Good connectivity throughout the area.

Final Thanks to Fauzan/Jeffy and Jenny to make my stay very very comfortable and assist me to get cab to go to various places.  I am working in a huge organization where many people travel a lot.  I have already started to recommend the stay.
title: A place for Chillaxing (Chill + Relaxing)

But no, they're going extra by giving us complimentary cakes to wish our son happy birthday 💕 Despite that Ms. Jenny was my acquaintance, she really don't have to do that. But she did and i'm so thankful for it🤎 she even did this even though she's on her day off, it's very thoughtful not only for Ms. Jenny but also for all Ashley's team🥺 these little things is the reason I'll come back to Ashley next time I decided to stay✨ so, thankyou Ashley for giving me and my family a very pleasant stay experience! Will surely come back for another staycation 😍 

P.S.: see, the birthday boy was very happy😆

text:
If you are thinking of a holiday/business trip in Jakarta, try this local hotel instead of international chains, which will provide a better value, also supporting local business at the same time.

These are speaking through my observations/experiences throughout my stay. 
1. All of front desk team can communicate in english quite well, and most of the staff can understand a little as well (would say better than most of the hotels in that area)
2. Excellent facilities - besides gym/pool, they have smart TV which has netflix, youtube etc you can even chromecast your device to the big screen. Love the JBL speaker in the gym (what’s better than gyming with ur fav jam) 
3. Great service - thanks to the hotel team (from front desk to housekeeping, valet) for the smile & greetings that never fails. Huge kudos to the front desk team which I think they are very well trained. They are prompt in addressing any issues you might have, and will try their best to help. 
4. Restaurant that serves authentic indonesian breakfast. Managed by another team - Adele, but well coordinated with the hotel management.
5. Good location - near to everything but also provide some quietness in the central of the city. Good security as well.

This hotel is quite new, which explains the good facilities. Hope that things maintained well. Will come back if I visit Jakarta again.
title: Highly recommend - - either family/couple/solo/business

text:
Arrived 2 hours after check in. They stated check in is not available for your room right now as they were busy before. So we sat in the restaurant for 35 minutes until the receptionist approached us and stated they have upgraded our room due to the inconvenience which was a good gesture for the long travel and stress the issue had caused regarding check in. 

Restaurant: depends which waiter you get, some of the waiters are nice, some are rude. You order drinks and you’ll wait a good 15 minutes before you get your Coca Cola in a can. Sometimes when you order Coca Cola( your drinks order ) they ask you if you want to order drinks, when you already have so that makes the drink waiting time longer. ( grabbed a glass and drank water out of the pool at the point in desperation).

Food is nice to be honest. 

The room nothing much different than a holiday inn to be honest, it’s nice but just standard. 

Overall I would stay here again if I had to, but I wouldn’t recommend anyone to stay here. Average hotel, average service, nice food. 

Do not leave outside of the Hotel as it is not very turiost Friendly unlike Bali. Always get a taxi, ( get a Indonesian sim and download and sign up to GRAB app( similar to UBER) . Cheaper fairs and you don’t get mugged. 

Hope this helps.
